item.title: By: Foton

item.description:
Guildmate claims that CT-Raid Assist is adding to the video lag in WoW. Dunno if that's true, but I do know that CTRA is my shepherd, I shall not want -- I don't leave home without it.
EDIT: Hey, speak of the devil, <a href="http://www.ctmod.net/downloads.ct">CTRA is updated to 1.501</a>, maybe there was something to that.
EDIT02: Make that CTRA 1.502.
